{"data":[{"name":"56:1","price":"1. Apabila terjadi hari Kiamat,","arabic":"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4980,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:2","price":"2. Terjadinya tidak dapat didustakan (disangkal).","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لِوَقۡعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4981,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:3","price":"3. (Kejadian itu) merendahkan (satu golongan) dan meninggikan (golongan yang lain).","arabic":"خَافِضَةٞ رَّافِعَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4982,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:4","price":"4. Apabila bumi diguncangkan sedahsyat-dahsyatnya,","arabic":"إِذَا رُجَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ رَجّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4983,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:5","price":"5. dan gunung-gunung dihancurluluhkan sehancur-hancurnya,","arabic":"وَبُسَّتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ بَسّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4984,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:6","price":"6. Maka jadilah ia debu yang beterbangan,","arabic":"فَكَانَتۡ هَبَآءٗ مُّنۢبَثّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4985,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:7","price":"7. Dan kamu menjadi tiga golongan,","arabic":"وَكُنتُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا ثَلَٰثَةٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4986,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:8","price":"8. Yaitu golongan kanan,*(825) alangkah mulianya golongan kanan itu,","arabic":"فَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4987,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"*825). Orang-orang yang menerima buku catatan amal mereka dengan tangan kanan.","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:9","price":"9. Dan golongan kiri,*(826) alangkah sengsaranya golongan kiri itu,","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4988,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"*826). Orang-orang yang menerima buku catatan amal mereka dengan tangan kiri.","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:10","price":"10. dan orang-orang yang paling dahulu (beriman), merekalah yang paling dahulu (masuk surga),","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ ٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4989,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:11","price":"11. Mereka itulah orang yang didekatkan (kepada Allah),","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4990,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:12","price":"12. berada dalam surga kenikmatan,","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4991,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:13","price":"13. Segolongan besar dari orang-orang yang terdahulu,*(827)","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4992,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"*827). Seluruh umat nabi-nabi sebelum Nabi Muhammad -ṣallallāhu 'alaihi wa sallam- dan yang dimaksud dengan orang yang kemudian ialah umat Nabi Muhammad -ṣallallāhu 'alaihi wa sallam-","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:14","price":"14. Dan segolongan kecil dari orang-orang yang kemudian,","arabic":"وَقَلِيلٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4993,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:15","price":"15. Mereka berada di atas dipan-dipan yang bertahtahkan emas dan permata,","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّوۡضُونَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4994,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:16","price":"16. Mereka bersandar di atasnya berhadap-hadapan.","arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَيۡهَا مُتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4995,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:17","price":"17. Mereka dikelilingi oleh anak-anak muda yang tetap muda,","arabic":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وِلۡدَٰنٞ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4996,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:18","price":"18. Dengan membawa gelas, cerek, dan sloki (piala) berisi minuman yang diambil dari air yang mengalir,","arabic":"بِأَكۡوَابٖ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4997,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:19","price":"19. Mereka tidak pening karenanya dan tidak pula mabuk,","arabic":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنۡهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4998,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:20","price":"20. Dan buah-buahan apapun yang mereka pilih,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4999,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:21","price":"21. Dan daging burung apa pun yang mereka inginkan,","arabic":"وَلَحۡمِ طَيۡرٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5000,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:22","price":"22. Dan ada bidadari-bidadari yang bermata indah,","arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5001,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:23","price":"23. Laksana mutiara yang tersimpan baik.","arabic":"كَأَمۡثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤۡلُوِٕ ٱلۡمَكۡنُونِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5002,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:24","price":"24. Sebagai balasan atas apa yang mereka kerjakan.","arabic":"جَزَآءَۢ بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5003,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:25","price":"25. Di sana mereka tidak mendengar percakapan yang sia-sia maupun yang menimbulkan dosa,","arabic":"لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5004,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:26","price":"26. Tetapi mereka mendengar ucapan salam.","arabic":"إِلَّا قِيلٗا سَلَٰمٗا سَلَٰمٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5005,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:27","price":"27. Dan golongan kanan, alangkah mulianya golongan kanan itu.","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5006,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:28","price":"28. (Mereka) berada di antara pohon bidara yang tidak berduri,","arabic":"فِي سِدۡرٖ مَّخۡضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5007,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:29","price":"29. Dan pohon pisang yang bersusun-susun (buahnya),","arabic":"وَطَلۡحٖ مَّنضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5008,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:30","price":"30. Dan naungan yang terbentang luas,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مَّمۡدُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5009,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:31","price":"31. Dan air yang mengalir terus-menerus,","arabic":"وَمَآءٖ مَّسۡكُوبٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5010,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:32","price":"32. Dan buah-buahan yang banyak,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ كَثِيرَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5011,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:33","price":"33. Yang tidak berhenti berbuah dan tidak terlarang mengambilnya,","arabic":"لَّا مَقۡطُوعَةٖ وَلَا مَمۡنُوعَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5012,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:34","price":"34. Dan kasur-kasur yang tebal lagi empuk.","arabic":"وَفُرُشٖ مَّرۡفُوعَةٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5013,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:35","price":"35. Kami menciptakan mereka (bidadari-bidadari itu) secara langsung,*(828)","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأۡنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5014,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"*828). Mereka diciptakan tanpa melalui kelahiran dan langsung menjadi gadis.","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:36","price":"36. Lalu Kami jadikan mereka perawan-perawan,","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُنَّ أَبۡكَارًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5015,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:37","price":"37. Yang penuh cinta (dan) sebaya umurnya,","arabic":"عُرُبًا أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5016,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:38","price":"38. Untuk golongan kanan,","arabic":"لِّأَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5017,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:39","price":"39. Segolongan besar dari orang-orang yang terdahulu,","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5018,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:40","price":"40. segolongan besar pula dari orang yang kemudian.","arabic":"وَثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5019,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:41","price":"41. Dan golongan kiri, alangkah sengsaranya golongan kiri itu.","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5020,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:42","price":"42. (Mereka) dalam siksaan angin yang sangat panas dan air yang mendidih,","arabic":"فِي سَمُومٖ وَحَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5021,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:43","price":"43. Dan naungan asap yang hitam,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مِّن يَحۡمُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5022,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:44","price":"44. Tidak sejuk dan tidak menyenangkan.","arabic":"لَّا بَارِدٖ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5023,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:45","price":"45. Sesungguhnya mereka sebelum itu (dahulu) hidup bermewah-mewah,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ قَبۡلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتۡرَفِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5024,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:46","price":"46. Dan mereka terus-menerus mengerjakan dosa yang besar,","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلۡحِنثِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5025,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:47","price":"47. Dan mereka berkata, “Apabila kami sudah mati, menjadi tanah dan tulang-belulang, apakah kami benar-benar akan dibangkitkan kembali?","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5026,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:48","price":"48. Apakah nenek moyang kami yang teradahulu (dibangkitkan pula)?”","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5027,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:49","price":"49. Katakanlah, “(Ya), sesungguhnya orang-orang yang terdahulu dan yang kemudian,","arabic":"قُلۡ إِنَّ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5028,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:50","price":"50. Pasti semua akan dikumpulkan pada waktu tertentu, pada hari yang sudah dimaklumi.","arabic":"لَمَجۡمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوۡمٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5029,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:51","price":"51. Kemudian sesungguhnya kamu, wahai orang-orang yang sesat lagi mendustakan!","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّكُمۡ أَيُّهَا ٱلضَّآلُّونَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5030,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:52","price":"52. pasti akan memakan pohon zaqqūm,*(829)","arabic":"لَأٓكِلُونَ مِن شَجَرٖ مِّن زَقُّومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5031,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"*829). Jenis pohon di neraka yang mengakibatkan derita luar biasa bagi yang memakannya.","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:53","price":"53. Maka akan penuh perutmu dengannya.","arabic":"فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5032,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:54","price":"54. Setelah itu kamu akan meminum air yang sangat panas.","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ عَلَيۡهِ مِنَ ٱلۡحَمِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5033,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:55","price":"55. Maka kamu minum seperti unta (yang sangat haus minum).","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ شُرۡبَ ٱلۡهِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5034,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:56","price":"56. Itulah hidangan untuk mereka pada hari pembalasan.”","arabic":"هَٰذَا نُزُلُهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5035,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:57","price":"57. Kami telah menciptakan kamu, mengapa kamu tidak membenarkan (hari berbangkit)?","arabic":"نَحۡنُ خَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ فَلَوۡلَا تُصَدِّقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5036,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:58","price":"58. Maka adakah kamu perhatikan, tentang (benih manusia) yang kamu pancarkan.","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تُمۡنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5037,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:59","price":"59. Kamukah yang menciptakannya, ataukah Kami penciptanya?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَخۡلُقُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5038,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:60","price":"60. Kami telah menentukan kematian masing-masing kamu dan Kami tidak lemah,","arabic":"نَحۡنُ قَدَّرۡنَا بَيۡنَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5039,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:61","price":"61. Untuk menggantikan kamu dengan orang-orang seperti kamu (di dunia) dan membangkitkan kamu kelak (di akhirat) dalam keadaan yang tidak kamu ketahui.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ أَمۡثَٰلَكُمۡ وَنُنشِئَكُمۡ فِي مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5040,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:62","price":"62. Dan sungguh, kamu telah tahu penciptaan yang pertama, mengapa kamu tidak mengambil pelajaran?","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمۡتُمُ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ فَلَوۡلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5041,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:63","price":"63. Pernahkah kamu perhatikan benih yang kamu tanam?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تَحۡرُثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5042,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:64","price":"64. Kamukah yang menumbuhkannya ataukah Kami yang menumbuhkan?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَزۡرَعُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلزَّٰرِعُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5043,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:65","price":"65. Sekiranya Kami kehendaki, niscaya Kami hancurkan sampai lumat; maka kamu akan tercengang,","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ لَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ حُطَٰمٗا فَظَلۡتُمۡ تَفَكَّهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5044,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:66","price":"66. (Sambil berkata), “Sungguh, kami benar-benar menderita kerugian,","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمُغۡرَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5045,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:67","price":"67. Bahkan kami tidak mendapat hasil apa pun.”","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5046,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:68","price":"68. Pernahkan kamu memperhatikan air yang kamu minum?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَآءَ ٱلَّذِي تَشۡرَبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5047,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:69","price":"69. Kamukah yang menurunkannya dari awan ataukah Kami yang menurunkan?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنزَلۡتُمُوهُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُزۡنِ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنزِلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5048,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:70","price":"70. Sekiranya Kami menghendaki, niscaya Kami menjadikannya asin, mengapa kamu tidak bersyukur?","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ جَعَلۡنَٰهُ أُجَاجٗا فَلَوۡلَا تَشۡكُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5049,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:71","price":"71. Maka pernahkah kamu memperhatikan tentang api yang kamu nyalakan (dengan kayu)?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلنَّارَ ٱلَّتِي تُورُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5050,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:72","price":"72. Kamukah yang menumbuhkan kayu itu ataukah kami yang menumbuhkan?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5051,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:73","price":"73. Kami menjadikannya (api itu) untuk peringatan dan bahan yang berguna bagi musafir.","arabic":"نَحۡنُ جَعَلۡنَٰهَا تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَمَتَٰعٗا لِّلۡمُقۡوِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5052,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:74","price":"74. Maka bertasbihlah dengan (menyebut) nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahabesar.","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5053,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:75","price":"75. Lalu Aku bersumpah dengan tempat beredarnya bintang-bintang.","arabic":"۞ فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَوَٰقِعِ ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5054,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:76","price":"76. Dan sesungguhnya itu benar-benar sumpah yang besar sekiranya kamu mengetahui,","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَقَسَمٞ لَّوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عَظِيمٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5055,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:77","price":"77. (Ini) sesungguhnya Al-Qur`ān yang sangat mulia,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقُرۡءَانٞ كَرِيمٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5056,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:78","price":"78. Dalam kitab yang terpelihara (Lauḥ Maḥfuẓ),","arabic":"فِي كِتَٰبٖ مَّكۡنُونٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5057,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:79","price":"79. Tidak ada yang menyentuhnya selain hamba-hamba yang disucikan.","arabic":"لَّا يَمَسُّهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡمُطَهَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5058,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:80","price":"80. Diturunkan dari Tuhan seluruh alam.","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5059,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:81","price":"81. Apakah kamu menganggap remeh berita ini (Al-Qur`ān)?","arabic":"أَفَبِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ أَنتُم مُّدۡهِنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5060,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:82","price":"82. Dan kamu menjadikan rezeki yang kamu terima (dari Allah) justru untuk mendustakan(-Nya).","arabic":"وَتَجۡعَلُونَ رِزۡقَكُمۡ أَنَّكُمۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5061,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:83","price":"83. Maka kalau begitu mengapa (tidak mencegah) ketika (nyawa) telah sampai di kerongkongan,","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلۡحُلۡقُومَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5062,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:84","price":"84. Dan kamu ketika itu melihat,","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ حِينَئِذٖ تَنظُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5063,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:85","price":"85. Dan Kami lebih dekat kepadanya daripada kamu, tetapi kamu tidak melihat,","arabic":"وَنَحۡنُ أَقۡرَبُ إِلَيۡهِ مِنكُمۡ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5064,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:86","price":"86. Maka mengapa jika kamu memang tidak dikuasai (oleh Allah),","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ غَيۡرَ مَدِينِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5065,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:87","price":"87. Kamu tidak mengembalikannya (nyawa itu) jika kamu orang yang benar?","arabic":"تَرۡجِعُونَهَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5066,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:88","price":"88. Jika dia (orang yang mati) itu termasuk didekatkan (kepada Allah),","arabic":"فَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5067,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:89","price":"89. maka dia memperoleh ketenteraman dan rezeki serta surga (yang penuh) kenikmatan.","arabic":"فَرَوۡحٞ وَرَيۡحَانٞ وَجَنَّتُ نَعِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5068,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:90","price":"90. Dan adapun jika dia termasuk golongan kanan,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5069,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:91","price":"91. Maka, “Salam bagimu, karena kamu dari golongan kanan!” (sambut malaikat).","arabic":"فَسَلَٰمٞ لَّكَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5070,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:92","price":"92. Dan adapun jika dia termasuk golongan orang yang mendustakan dan sesat,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5071,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:93","price":"93. Maka dia disambut siraman air yang mendidih,","arabic":"فَنُزُلٞ مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5072,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:94","price":"94. Dan dibakar di dalam neraka.","arabic":"وَتَصۡلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5073,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:95","price":"95. Sungguh, inilah keyakinan yang benar.","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ حَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5074,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"56:96","price":"96. Maka bertasbihlah dengan (menyebut) nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahabesar.","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5075,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah","Chapter Al-Waqi'ah","Waqi'ah","Surah Waqi'ah","Chapter Waqi'ah","Al Waqi'ah","Surah Al Waqi'ah","Chapter Al Waqi'ah","Surah 56","Chapter 56","The Inevitable","الواقعة"]}